As the requestor of this ticket I am satisfied that a) the need is
appropriate b) technical and process solutions can be developed to provide
this capability.

I  am now asking for this ticket to be closed. Tomorrow I will talk to Rob
Quick and ask for the capability for non-WLCG MOU&#39;d VOs to report to the
APEL accounting repository to be a task under Operations and to talk to him
about what might be needed to provide the capability.

thank you to all for following up on the ticket

Ruth

