Have marked this pending since any action is pending a policy decision from OSG management before we can do anything.

Thanks,
timm

Summary&#58; FootPrints Ticket Description&#58;

We wish to publish ILC VO information to APEL. The list of OSG VO&#39;s which gets published to APEL is controlled on our end. There is a list of VO&#39;s on the gratia machine which can be edited to add more VO&#39;s. There is nothing John Gordon or his people can do to add ILC. However, John W. tells me that that reporting is done only for sites which are signatories to the WLCG MOU. FermiGrid, the main site on which the ILC VO runs, is not a signatory.

This exposes an policy issue within OSG which needs to be resolved.

For complete ticket details, click

<a href='https&#58;//ticket.grid.iu.edu/goc/11283' target='_blank' rel='nofollow'>https&#58;//ticket.grid.iu.edu/goc/11283</a>
Click here to view Incident&#58; INC000000167804

